        <title type="html"><![CDATA[我走过的杭州景区（一)]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-yi/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-yi/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-08-15T10:06:55.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>一、西湖，杭州的代名词，不同时候的西湖，犹如不同打扮的西子</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>冬日清晨的断桥<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d22b81cea53705cc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>雨夜的断桥，人依旧那么多<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/3726da19a9c1d1a0.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>夜色来临的西湖<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/e6dfa6ac1c5b91b4.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>茅家埠，西湖边没那么热闹却依然保有西湖风景的景点<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d11525e3856c02e9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>黛色参天,辅以太极八卦<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/72065ae89b5f238b.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>偶遇湖边的茅草亭<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d7c17b35d05156f9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>斑驳的通利古桥，在一旁见证着岁月流逝<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/95446ce7505fbe54.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>西湖落日，伴有秋天大雁南飞<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2c24a91f6386ef63.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>晚秋的西湖和断桥<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/9f952d2daf3bb9c9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>深秋早晨的虎跑路，也是我的上班路，形色匆匆</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141559.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>深秋的景区随拍<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/82da6bcc56722a35.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>深秋的西湖边，虽秋风肃杀，却挡不住远处的游人如织<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2c81dfe74753fec4.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>纸币上的三潭印月了解一下<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/24b8af63d833fd1d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>三潭映月岛上风光<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/1f78ee530a31b695.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2f8bc528a5847f85.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>雪夜西湖边<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b063d265aed740a2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/3fad3f7368ffcf08.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>雪夜的宝石山上<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/90cc5271ffcf6efb.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>二、西溪湿地，杭州的肺</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>大雪后的湿地，银装素裹<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/770af3e72f807775.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b8354dea68aaec32.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>在冬日暖阳下的西溪湿地中，度过2016年的最后一天，见证着这一年最后的落日</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/268f892086787cd1.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/fb0847419cb20802.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>春日里，在西溪湿地泛舟，看河边的建筑，望船头的河道</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/cbbf2ec58beba67f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/96de7509a2ebc202.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>三、灵隐寺，杭州名刹</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>飞来峰口<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/af5e0f9d0fb0cb6b.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>理公之塔，底部覆钵、仰莲刹座，上承宝珠、宝瓶，集佛教史迹、造塔艺术、佛像雕刻于一体<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/f965221040e4f8bc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>刻于山体上的多宝天王<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/784f3d46b9a74d2f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>济公殿<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/4bfafcb06def5e4f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>香火鼎盛的大雄宝殿<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/dabbccf2c8cea820.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>四、钱江新城，不仅仅是杭州新地标</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>国庆节，向祖国母亲致敬<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/8b0f2364faacdfd0.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>大金球<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b12173cc3c184512.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>可爱的熊猫出镜<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/963ef351b9d2c130.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>动漫人物出场<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/8a29c9d636cccea5.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>灯光、音乐、喷泉的完美呼应<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/019e3201c57fa560.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>城市阳台上完美的远眺<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b895658efa0d2a90.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>五、青芝坞和植物园</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>青芝坞<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/cadee6094a8664e4.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>植物园的梅花<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/cec917a38c8dbfe5.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/4a1d2a19a082d28d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/45c8e10c516d4c6d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>六、临安大明山，明王朝的龙兴之地</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>景区门口乱入的小黄人<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/985190125ad0ad30.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>明王朝的印记<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/882247c6ce326ae2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>一路上山势险峻，不愧是当年明太祖的藏兵之地<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/0d5ef03120bd6a96.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/220948dd7da6d6c2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>路遇悬崖上的松树，有点迎客松的味道<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/a82bc876a5d20388.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>栈桥上，一边是巍峨的山势，一边是万丈深的悬崖<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/4efb2a67980c87ed.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>镌刻有“潜龙隐德”的小瀑布<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/6bbc1b793f350b81.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>六、宋城，一个可以穿越的地方</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>这是一个让你回到千年前的地方，不知道回去后的我们都是什么身份<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/51209a9306d2b289.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/9ced650d3be71fc2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>老匠人默默地产生艺术品<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/cc4db220b4688fe9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>震撼的南宋千古情情景剧<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/19ac8a31a1660345.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>偶遇爱情广场，下次容我带妹子来再逛<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/680434126eb7e1cc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>下一篇：<a href="https://note.xuejian.site/web/#/page/28" title="我走过的杭州景区（二）">我走过的杭州景区（二）</a></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[移动副卡实现单卡iphone双卡双待]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xuejian.site/post/yi-dong-fu-qia-shi-xian-dan-qia-iphone-shuang-qia-shuang-dai/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/yi-dong-fu-qia-shi-xian-dan-qia-iphone-shuang-qia-shuang-dai/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-06-19T09:44:46.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><font size=3>国行新出的iPhone XR和iPhone XS MAX的双卡功能的确让众多单卡iPhone用户羡慕，毕竟在中国，由于各种原因，很多人都有两张或以上的号卡。其实，如果其中一张为移动卡，则可以借助中国移动集团下各专业公司的APP，间接实现单卡iPhone的双卡双待，或者是国行iPhone XR和iPhone XS MAX的三卡三待。</p>
<p><font size=4>一、app store下载相关app及准备对应的微信小程序</p>
<p><font size=3>1、无忧行。无忧行是中国移动为出境游用户推出的出境游通讯服务门户APP，这里我们主要利用其可以免费转接移动卡的电话和短信。该软件如果通过蒲公英下载企业版，可以提供电话界面直接接听的功能，无需像微信一样弹出对话框后点入接听，企业版二维码如下，或者点击链接：<a href="http://www.pgyer.com/K5qj" title="无忧行企业版">无忧行企业版</a>。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://www.pgyer.com/app/qrcode/K5qj" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>注：如果下载的是无忧行的企业版，需要按以下路径确认企业证书：设置-通用-设备管理-企业级应用，进入后点击信任该证书。</p>
<p><font size=3>2、和飞信。由于无忧行在境内无法直接回复短信和电话，因此短信可以通过和飞信回复。同时，和飞信每月赠送100分钟通话，可以解决一部分电话需求；</p>
<p><font size=3>3、密友圈。密友圈为和飞信的子品牌，其优势是可以设置10个中国移动的号码为不限时长拨打号码，同时赠送100分钟通话，解决一部分电话需求；</p>
<p><font size=3>4、微信小程序“聊会儿”。该小程序为中移互联网公司推出，需要每天签到获取通话分钟数，差不多每个月有300至400分钟；</p>
<p><font size=3>5、（可选）微信小程序“机伶”。该小程序为浙江移动推出，因此仅适用于浙江移动。该小程序提供运营商端的骚扰拦截功能，防止托管在无忧行的移动号码骚然电话或短信过多。</p>
<p><font size=4>二、无忧行设置方法。</p>
<p><font size=3>双卡双待是否可以实现，核心在无忧行的设置，具体设置方法如下图：</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1902/67e988755a50182e.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[自建低成本大流量图床]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xuejian.site/post/zi-jian-di-cheng-ben-da-liu-liang-tu-chuang/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/zi-jian-di-cheng-ben-da-liu-liang-tu-chuang/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-06-19T08:49:47.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><font size=4>一、建立阿里云香港区OSS Bucket</p>
<p><font size=3>1、建立阿里云香港区的OSS Bucket，注意点是红框标注的两处，区域选择香港，读写权限选择公共读；</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531155034.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>2、记录红框标注的地址，后续备用；</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531155834.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4>二、购买阿里云香港区域轻量服务器并安装nginx</p>
<p><font size=3>1、购买阿里云香港区轻量服务器，注意区域选择香港，预装使用宝塔（因为这个不会预装任何web服务器），使用量不高选择默认的套餐即可，然后一路点击完成付款即可；</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531160615.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>2、完全付款后，可以在服务器界面看到购买的服务器，待状态完成后点击红框标注的图标，启动远程连接;</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531161505.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>3、在跳出的界面输入命令:suo -s，进入root用户；</p>
<p><font size=3>4、打开nginx的淘宝网开源版Tengine的下载页面，选择最新版本：<a href="http://tengine.taobao.org/download_cn.html" title="Tengine下载页面">Tengine下载页面</a> ，右击选择红框标注的“复制链接地址”</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531162725.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>5、在web界面执行以下命令</p>
<pre><code class="language-shell">wget http://tengine.taobao.org/download/tengine-2.3.0.tar.gz
tar -zxvf tengine-2.3.0.tar.gz
cd tengine-2.3.0
./configure
make
make install
</code></pre>
<p><font size=3>6、使用命令打开nginx的配置文件</p>
<pre><code class="language-shell">vi /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf
</code></pre>
<p><font size=3>在如图下方输入红框标注的信息：include vhost/*.conf;</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531164458.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>7、使用以下命令建立文件夹和配置文件：</p>
<pre><code class="language-shell">mkdir /usr/local/nginx/conf/vhost
cd /usr/local/nginx/conf/vhost
vi picture.conf
</code></pre>
<p><font size=3>8、picture.conf的模版，请注意按照注释内容更改</p>
<pre><code class="language-shell">server
 {
 listen 80;
 listen 443 ssl;
 ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2;
 ssl_certificate /etc/nginx/ssl/xxx.pem; //需要申请HTTPS证书后，根据证书名字提供
 ssl_certificate_key /etc/nginx/ssl/xxx.key;
    server_name picture.xxx.com;  //这里填写域名
    location / {
	    client_max_body_size 100m;
        #proxy_set_header Host $host;
        #proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        #proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_pass https://xxx.oss-cn-hongkong-internal.aliyuncs.com; 
		//这里的url填写第一部分记录下来的OSS内网地址
    }
    #access_log logs/note.log;
    access_log /dev/null;
}

</code></pre>
<p><font size=3>9、使用以下命令启动nginx</p>
<pre><code class="language-shell">/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx
</code></pre>
<p><font size=4>三、设置阿里云子账户</p>
<p><font size=3>1、点击搜索阿里云的“访问控制”，进入子账户设置</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531170302.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>2、按图示步骤点击，进入添加用户环节</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531170626.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>3、这个界面输入想用的用户名，然后只勾选红框标注“编程访问”</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531170905.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>4、记录该页面的各类用户信息，下载红框标注的文件并保存csv备用，完成后点击后退</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531171141.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>5、在该界面点击刚刚创建的用户，进入用户权限设置；</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531171518.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>6、搜索“AliyunOSSFullAccess”，点击唯一选项添加后点击确认，效果如下图：</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531171735.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4>四、设置上传工具</p>
<p><font size=3>1、下载上传工具PicGo，下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo/releases" title="PicGo下载界面">PicGo下载界面</a></p>
<p><font size=3>2、按图示的步骤打开阿里云OSS设置，并按第三部分记录的子账户信息填入，自定义域名设置为第二部分nginx上写入的域名，最后点击确认并点击设置为默认图床</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531172659.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>3、完成后，可以在上传区上传图片试试，默认链接为markdown链接，可以工具自己的需求进行更改。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190531172730.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
]]></content>
